Package civitas.celestis.math.vector

Class GenericVector

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.math.vector.GenericVector
All Implemented Interfaces:
Number, Vector, Iterable<Double>
public class GenericVector extends Object implements Vector, Iterable<Double>

GenericVector

This class represents a generic vector with double values. It implements the Vector interface and provides various operations for vector arithmetic, including addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. The vector can be created with an array of values. It supports element-wise operations and deep copying.
